* email
* passwordHash
* role
* activeIssueCount

#### 📁 Project

* name
* slug
* members
* bugCount

#### 🐞 Bug

* title
* status
* severity
* priority
* assignedTo
* reportedBy
* stepsToReproduce

#### 🔔 Notification

* message
* userId
* type
* isRead

---

### 🔗 Relationships

* Bug → Project
* Bug → User (assigned/reported)
* Project → Users

---

## 🔄 6. End-to-End Flow

### 🧪 Example: Create Bug

1. User fills form (Frontend)
2. API call → `/bugs`
3. Backend:

   * Auth check
   * Role validation
   * AI duplicate detection
4. Save in DB
5. Update project bug count
6. Send response
7. Trigger socket notification

---

